These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, cola
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, motorbike
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person driving the snowmobile##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage          | sprite      | fanta        | cola     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Transport         | snowmobile  | train      | motorbike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, coach, photographer
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, photography
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, poppy
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the coach##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the coach is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the photographer is in an even position##4
7. the person who growspoppy is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | coach    | photographer | accountant |
| Hobby   | board-games | filmmaking       | photography   |
| Pet           | hamster  | guinea-pig   | ferret     |
| Flower         | orchid | poppy       | dahlia   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, turkish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, turtle
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, pop, jazz
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the turkish is the fan of jazz##1
3. the colombian is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the american is between the person watching adventure movies and the fan of jazz##2
5. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the turtle is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Nationality          | turkish | american | colombian |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | action | adventure |
| Pet           | pony       | bird   | turtle    |
| Music-Genre     | jazz      | disco   | pop |

