The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, crime
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, goldfish
There are 3 different nationalities: german, mexican, polish
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the german##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the polish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | water     | juice   | coffee         |
| Movie-Genre           | family | martial-arts | crime |
| Pet   | goldfish      | bird   | hedgehog            |
| Nationality   | mexican   | polish  | german         |

