.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cauliflower, raspberry
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, begonia
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, traveling, writing
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person eating cauliflower##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Food          | raspberry    | asparagus     | cauliflower |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | begonia | bellflower      |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | mystery       | disaster    |
| Hobby   | traveling      | reading         | writing     |

