.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, emerald, apricot
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, crime, zombie
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, metal, r&b
House: art-deco, futuristic, gothic-revival
1. the person who likes light-blue is in the middle##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is the futuristic house##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the fan of ambient is between the futuristic house and the person who likes emerald##2
7. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Color          | emerald | light-blue | apricot |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action    | zombie |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | ambient   | r&b    |
| House     | gothic-revival   | art-deco       | futuristic |

