.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, purple, lilac
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, dancing, sudoku
3 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, billiard
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram
1. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Color      | purple | grey    | lilac  |
| Hobby         | sudoku        | camping   | dancing   |
| Game   | billiard       | scrabble    | mah-jongg |
| Transport     | tram          | quad-bike | car       |

