.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, tea
City: hamburg, nizza, venice
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, horse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bongani, chaman
1. the chaman-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | tea       | soy-milk   | iced-tea |
| City   | hamburg | venice     | nizza |
| Pet           | bird      | chinchilla | horse    |
| Cigar         | bongani  | chaman     | swisher |

