.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, gospel
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indian, polish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, juice
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, trike
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person driving the trike##1
6. the indian is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
9. the indian is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre           | house | hip-hop   | gospel |
| Nationality   | argentine  | indian    | polish    |
| Beverage         | iced-tea    | milk | juice   |
| Transport     | motorbike  | trike     | airplane  |

