The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, rowing
1. the american is the cape-cod house##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person playing snooker and the ranch-style house##2
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the victorian house##1
6. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| House         | cape-cod    | victorian   | ranch-style      |
| Game           | snooker | mah-jongg    | go |
| Nationality   | american       | argentine | turkish      |
| Sport         | rowing         | parkour   | climbing     |

