.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-15::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, nectarine, pineapple
3 different pets are kept: dog, pony, rat
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, december, january
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, iced-tea
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Food        | nectarine | lettuce | pineapple |
| Pet         | dog       | pony    | rat       |
| Birthday       | december  | january | august      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | juice    | coffee |

