The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, epic, family
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, september, april
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, jet-ski
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Game          | canasta     | billiard   | backgammon     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | epic   | drama      |
| Birthday   | september | july | april    |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | boat   | helicopter |

