3. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Job          | entrepreneur     | police-officer | security-guard   |
| Pet         | snake   | cat | bird |
| Nationality   | pakistani | dutch       | colombian   |
| Transport     | train     | snowmobile  | taxi        |

