2. the person playing go is between the person playing domino and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
3. the person drinking coffee is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2        |     3      |
| Beverage      | coffee         | sprite         | milk       |
| Hobby         | chess          | camping        | filmmaking |
| Game           | domino | go | monopoly     |
| Cigar   | vegafina      | montecristo          | bongani     |

