2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Movie-Genre           | scientific  | horror | western   |
| Hobby   | writing | sudoku           | reading      |
| Pet           | mouse   | horse          | guinea-pig |
| Transport     | boat    | tram           | snowmobile |

 